				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3924cea elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="3924cea" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
			<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-medium"><span style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>1.2 What is my goal?</strong></span></h2>		</div>
				</div>
