				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6822992 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6822992" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p style="text-align: center;"><em>Figure 2.1 Rough visualization of project structure (data flow) &#8211; ^ v represent corresponding directions <br /></em></p></div>
