				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix"><p style="text-align: center;"><em>Figure 2.2 Roadmap of the project (Source: <span style="color: ##bff2ff;"><a style="color: ##bff2ff;" href="http://lucahohmann.com/magic-musicplayer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">lucahohmann.com</a></span>)</em></p></div>
